Name: Death courier
About the game: In 2340. Earth ravaged, nearly destroyed. The last cities try to keep themselves alive and not starve. Hard times ahead. The roads to the other cities are destroyed, devastated or besieged by bandits. Story You are postman 09. Your job is to bring parcels from one place to another. Gameplay Pick up your packages and bring them to the exit. Graphic A milestone in technology. With the Unreal Engine 4 we conjure breathtaking pictures on your screen. Enjoy sharp textures and rich colors. Explore Explore the open world of Death Courier. You are completely free. You decide where you want to go.
